(Sorry, but I didn't get to role play this guy, and the concept was bad)

:=
:Dachande/Dark Prime::

    Dachande finally reached shore. He loped around=
, and soon fell pray to a trap. He was knocked unconscious and when he awok=
e he saw Dark Prime looming over him.
    Dark Prime looked directly at him=
. "You are completely organic, yet it seems that you can Transform. We will=
 soon remedy that."
    Dachande had a look of terror in his eyes as Dark P=
rime fired the Key to Vector Sigma at him. He went Techno, and without a Sp=
ark soon started to die. Dark Prime let him loose and told him one thing.
 =
   "Go, now and warn the Maximals that Optimus Prime will be coming for the=
m soon."
    Dachande hobbled off hoping that these Maximals could help him=
. He walked a long way and soon came to what could only be the Maximal base=
.
    "Please, don't shoot," He said. "I need sanctuary."
    His primary s=
ystems were failing and he needed help emidatly. He fell to the ground and =
hoped that the Maximals would help him.
(Please, this is a Major part of my=
 story, You have to know that Dark Prime has the Key.)
